{"id":13858,"date":"2022-10-04T11:31:21","date_gmt":"2022-10-04T04:31:21","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=13858"},"modified":"2022-10-08T11:33:03","modified_gmt":"2022-10-08T04:33:03","slug":"o-to-can-kiem-tra-gi-sau-khi-qua-vung-ngap-nuoc","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/o-to-can-kiem-tra-gi-sau-khi-qua-vung-ngap-nuoc\/","title":{"rendered":"\u00d4 t\u00f4 c\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m tra g\u00ec sau khi qua v\u00f9ng ng\u1eadp n\u01b0\u1edbc?"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"article__sapo cms-desc\">Khi g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1eadp s\u00e2u, t\u00e0i x\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1o kh\u00f4ng cho \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u0111i qua v\u00ec ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb th\u1ee7y k\u00edch ho\u1eb7c &#8220;d\u00ednh&#8221; ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1c l\u1ed7i nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng kh\u00e1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eafc d\u0129 ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua khu v\u1ef1c l\u0169 l\u1ee5t, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0a xe \u0111i ki\u1ec3m tra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 &#8220;x\u1ebf c\u01b0ng&#8221;.<\/div>\n<div class=\"article__body cms-body\">\n<p>L\u00e1i xe qua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1eadp s\u00e2u r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 n\u1ebfu d\u00f2ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111ang ch\u1ea3y si\u1ebft v\u00ec ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb cu\u1ed1n tr\u00f4i. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00fac b\u1ea5y gi\u1edd. V\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u00e1c t\u00e0i x\u1ebf c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e1i xe qua v\u00f9ng n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1ebfu m\u1ef1c n\u01b0\u1edbc cao h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda chi\u1ec1u cao c\u1ee7a l\u1ed1p. L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed7 xe \u1edf n\u01a1i an to\u00e0n cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u00fat. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng n\u1eafm r\u00f5 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e2u, h\u00e3y quan s\u00e1t c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c.<\/p>\n<p>N\u1ebfu v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i l\u00e1i xe qua v\u00f9ng n\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u00e0i x\u1ebf c\u1ea7n h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng. \u0110i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n xe h\u01a1i v\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1eadp s\u00e2u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y h\u01b0 h\u1ecfng cho \u00f4 t\u00f4. Khi \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ch\u1ebft m\u00e1y, t\u00e0i x\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c v\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee7y k\u00edch. Ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1, ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0a \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c ti\u1ec7m s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa uy t\u00edn \u0111\u1ec3 xem x\u00e9t m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 chi ti\u1ebft trong danh s\u00e1ch sau \u0111\u00e2y, gi\u00fap k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Phanh<\/strong><\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_10_04\/brakes-60ec0ce10cb8f-9860.jpg\" data-desc=\"\u00d4 t\u00f4 c\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m tra g\u00ec sau khi qua v\u00f9ng ng\u1eadp n\u01b0\u1edbc?\" data-index=\"0\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_10_04\/brakes-60ec0ce10cb8f-9860.jpg\" alt=\"\u00d4 t\u00f4 c\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m tra g\u00ec sau khi qua v\u00f9ng ng\u1eadp n\u01b0\u1edbc? \u1ea3nh 1\" data-image-id=\"3335578\" data-width=\"650\" data-height=\"430\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_10_04\/brakes-60ec0ce10cb8f-9860.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu ph\u1ea3i xem x\u00e9t l\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng phanh v\u00ec b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng hao m\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00e1m sau n\u1ebfu b\u1ecb ng\u1ea5m n\u01b0\u1edbc. Sau khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u01a1n l\u0169, h\u00e3y t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1p phanh \u00f4 t\u00f4 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a n\u00f3. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng phanh tr\u00ean \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t khi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e1i xe. L\u01b0u \u00fd r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phanh g\u1ea5p v\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra va ch\u1ea1m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau.<\/p>\n<p><strong>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111i\u1ec7n<\/strong><\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_10_04\/car-electronics-60ec0dcd85fd6-694.jpg\" data-desc=\"\u00d4 t\u00f4 c\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m tra g\u00ec sau khi qua v\u00f9ng ng\u1eadp n\u01b0\u1edbc?\" data-index=\"1\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_10_04\/car-electronics-60ec0dcd85fd6-694.jpg\" alt=\"\u00d4 t\u00f4 c\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m tra g\u00ec sau khi qua v\u00f9ng ng\u1eadp n\u01b0\u1edbc? \u1ea3nh 2\" data-image-id=\"3335579\" data-width=\"650\" data-height=\"430\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_10_04\/car-electronics-60ec0dcd85fd6-694.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>N\u01b0\u1edbc c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00f4 t\u00f4 nh\u01b0 h\u1ed9p c\u1ea7u ch\u00ec v\u00e0 h\u1ed9p m\u00e1y t\u00ednh. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea7u n\u1ed1i \u0111i\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00f4 t\u00f4 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng h\u01a1i \u1ea9m s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 g\u00e2y ra c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p nh\u01b0 ch\u1eadp \u0111i\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p>V\u00ec v\u1eady, ch\u00fang ta n\u00ean ki\u1ec3m tra h\u1ed9p c\u1ea7u ch\u00ec v\u00e0 h\u1ed9p m\u00e1y t\u00ednh n\u1ebfu c\u1ea3 hai b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb \u01b0\u1edbt ho\u1eb7c b\u1ecb ng\u00e2m n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eb9 khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u0169. Khi c\u1ea7u ch\u00ec b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ee9t, ch\u1ee7 xe c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o ch\u00fa th\u00edch th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y tr\u00ean v\u1ecf h\u1ed9p c\u1ea7u ch\u00ec. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, n\u1ebfu h\u1ed9p m\u00e1y t\u00ednh b\u1ecb \u01b0\u1edbt, ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n lau b\u1eb1ng kh\u0103n s\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m.<\/p>\n<p><strong>B\u1ed9 ch\u1ebf h\u00f2a kh\u00ed<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng xe h\u01a1i c\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m tra b\u1ed9 ch\u1ebf h\u00f2a kh\u00ed c\u1ee7a \u00f4 t\u00f4 xem n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o qua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1eabn hay kh\u00f4ng. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e1i xe v\u00ec s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 h\u1ecfng n\u1eb7ng th\u00eam.<\/p>\n<p><strong>C\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t l\u1ecfng<\/strong><\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_10_04\/pexels-photo-8985459-5156.jpg\" data-desc=\"\u00d4 t\u00f4 c\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m tra g\u00ec sau khi qua v\u00f9ng ng\u1eadp n\u01b0\u1edbc?\" data-index=\"2\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_10_04\/pexels-photo-8985459-5156.jpg\" alt=\"\u00d4 t\u00f4 c\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m tra g\u00ec sau khi qua v\u00f9ng ng\u1eadp n\u01b0\u1edbc? \u1ea3nh 3\" data-image-id=\"3335584\" data-width=\"2520\" data-height=\"1418\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_10_04\/pexels-photo-8985459-5156.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>N\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00e0n v\u00e0o khoang \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 v\u00e0 l\u00e0m h\u1ecfng c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t l\u1ecfng quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 d\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1, d\u1ea7u h\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u1ecfng vi sai. V\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00e0i x\u1ebf c\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng que th\u0103m v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m tra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u1ea5t l\u1ecfng. N\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t trong c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb lo\u00e3ng, \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0u ho\u1eb7c tr\u1eafng \u0111\u1ee5c, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ch\u00fang \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec5m n\u01b0\u1edbc. Khi g\u1eb7p tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y, t\u00e0i x\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e1i xe ti\u1ebfp v\u00ec n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y h\u01b0 h\u1ecfng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.<\/p>\n<p><strong>N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t<\/strong><\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_10_04\/flooded-car-interior-60ec0e15f1d5d-7670.jpg\" data-desc=\"\u00d4 t\u00f4 c\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m tra g\u00ec sau khi qua v\u00f9ng ng\u1eadp n\u01b0\u1edbc?\" data-index=\"3\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_10_04\/flooded-car-interior-60ec0e15f1d5d-7670.jpg\" alt=\"\u00d4 t\u00f4 c\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m tra g\u00ec sau khi qua v\u00f9ng ng\u1eadp n\u01b0\u1edbc? \u1ea3nh 4\" data-image-id=\"3335580\" data-width=\"650\" data-height=\"430\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_10_04\/flooded-car-interior-60ec0e15f1d5d-7670.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng khu v\u1ef1c d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t. Vi\u1ec7c &#8220;nh\u1ea5n ch\u00ecm&#8221; \u00f4 t\u00f4 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho ph\u00e9p n\u01b0\u1edbc x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp qua c\u00e1c mi\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ec7m c\u1eeda ho\u1eb7c g\u1ea7m xe. \u0110\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng l\u0169 l\u1ee5t kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, t\u00e0i x\u1ebf c\u1ea7n th\u00e1o t\u1ea5m th\u1ea3m tr\u1ea3i s\u00e0n ra v\u00e0 s\u1edd xem t\u1ea5m th\u1ea3m tr\u1ea3i s\u00e0n c\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng. N\u1ebfu b\u1ecb \u01b0\u1edbt, h\u00e3y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c lau s\u1ea1ch, h\u00fat \u1ea9m v\u00e0 l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 khu v\u1ef1c n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. N\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ecdng b\u00ean trong khoang cabin qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u v\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m h\u1ecfng nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng th\u00f4ng tin gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a tr\u00ean \u00f4 t\u00f4.<\/p>\n<p><strong>G\u1ea7m xe<\/strong><\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_10_04\/hien-tuong-xe-o-to-ca-gam-va-bien-phap-khac-phuc-nhanh-gon-01-9053.jpg\" data-desc=\"\u00d4 t\u00f4 c\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m tra g\u00ec sau khi qua v\u00f9ng ng\u1eadp n\u01b0\u1edbc?\" data-index=\"4\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_10_04\/hien-tuong-xe-o-to-ca-gam-va-bien-phap-khac-phuc-nhanh-gon-01-9053.jpg\" alt=\"\u00d4 t\u00f4 c\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m tra g\u00ec sau khi qua v\u00f9ng ng\u1eadp n\u01b0\u1edbc? \u1ea3nh 5\" data-image-id=\"3335593\" data-width=\"1000\" data-height=\"667\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_10_04\/hien-tuong-xe-o-to-ca-gam-va-bien-phap-khac-phuc-nhanh-gon-01-9053.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>N\u1ebfu l\u00e1i xe qua v\u0169ng b\u00f9n, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao \u0111\u1ea5t, \u0111\u00e1, c\u1ecf, m\u1ea3nh v\u1ee5n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t b\u1ea9n s\u1ebd b\u00e1m v\u00e0o b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn g\u1ea7m. H\u00e3y ki\u1ec3m tra khoang m\u00e1y, b\u1ed9 t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t, g\u1ea7m xe v\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u1ea5m c\u1ea3n. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n tr\u00ean b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn n\u00e0o, c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch ch\u00fang c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. B\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n d\u00ednh v\u00e0o c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n kim lo\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u0103n m\u00f2n v\u00e0 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa t\u1ed1n k\u00e9m.<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u0110\u00e8n chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Ki\u1ec3m tra t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e8n chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e8n xi nhan \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft ch\u00fang c\u00f3 b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec5m n\u01b0\u1edbc hay kh\u00f4ng. C\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n b\u1ecb h\u1ecfng s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay th\u1ebf n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch ho\u1eb7c s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, t\u00e0i x\u1ebf c\u1ea7n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh camera sau v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 xe v\u1eabn \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1<\/strong><\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_10_04\/pexels-photo-12658309-1541.jpg\" data-desc=\"\u00d4 t\u00f4 c\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m tra g\u00ec sau khi qua v\u00f9ng ng\u1eadp n\u01b0\u1edbc?\" data-index=\"5\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_10_04\/pexels-photo-12658309-1541.jpg\" alt=\"\u00d4 t\u00f4 c\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m tra g\u00ec sau khi qua v\u00f9ng ng\u1eadp n\u01b0\u1edbc? \u1ea3nh 6\" data-image-id=\"3335595\" data-width=\"2250\" data-height=\"1500\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_10_04\/pexels-photo-12658309-1541.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>N\u1ebfu nghe th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eeb khoang m\u00e1y, g\u1ea7m xe, \u1ed1ng x\u1ea3, h\u00e3y \u0111\u01b0a xe \u0111\u1ebfn gara. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111i\u1ec1u tra v\u00e0 s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi, ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng thi\u1ec7t h\u1ea1i l\u1edbn \u0111i k\u00e8m h\u00f3a \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1eaft \u0111\u1ecf.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Khi g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1eadp s\u00e2u, t\u00e0i x\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1o kh\u00f4ng cho \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u0111i qua v\u00ec ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb th\u1ee7y k\u00edch ho\u1eb7c &#8220;d\u00ednh&#8221; ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1c l\u1ed7i nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng kh\u00e1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eafc d\u0129 ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua khu v\u1ef1c l\u0169 l\u1ee5t, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0a xe \u0111i ki\u1ec3m tra [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":13794,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1,30],"tags":[],"yst_prominent_words":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13858"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=13858"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13858\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":13859,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13858\/revisions\/13859"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/13794"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=13858"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=13858"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=13858"},{"taxonomy":"yst_prominent_words","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/yst_prominent_words?post=13858"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}